'''BMW R1200RT'''系列 是一款[[BMW|BMW]] 2005年上市的巡航機車 用以取代R1150RT系列. 具有1170cc[[水平對向引擎|水平對向引擎]]和六段變速 .<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.vosa.gov.uk/vosa/apps/recalls/searches/expand.asp?uniqueID=7802F713BF36E6898025713B003ECCD2 | title= Recall RM/2006/020 | publisher= [[Vehicle_and_Operator_Services_Agency|VOSA]] | date= 14 March 2006 | accessdate= 7 January 2009 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110614135431/http://www.vosa.gov.uk/vosa/apps/recalls/searches/expand.asp?uniqueID=7802F713BF36E6898025713B003ECCD2 | archive-date= 2011-06-14 | dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.vosa.gov.uk/vosa/apps/recalls/searches/expand.asp?uniqueID=3931D4B7E0CCF9208025713B003F3828&freeText=Blank | title= Recall RM/2006/021 | publisher= [[Vehicle_and_Operator_Services_Agency|VOSA]] | date= 14 March 2006 | accessdate= 7 January 2009 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110614135441/http://www.vosa.gov.uk/vosa/apps/recalls/searches/expand.asp?uniqueID=3931D4B7E0CCF9208025713B003F3828&freeText=Blank | archive-date= 2011-06-14 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>
配備雙點火防震爆BMS-K引擎電子管理系統和採用兩個氧氣探測器的三重觸式催化器，0-100km/h只需3.6秒，[[EVO|EVO]]動力輔助掣動、綜合式[[防锁死刹车系统|ABS]]煞車系統，油缸容量27[[公升|公升]]90km/h巡航每一百公里只需3.6公升油耗，香港售價約20萬[[港幣|港幣]]。

其特別版本被大量配置在[[澳洲|澳洲]]的[[維多利亞州|維多利亞州]]州警以及[[英國|英國]]地方警察部隊。

